contentfulProduct.name: Lamb & Rice Paté
contentfulProduct.teaser: Lamb and Rice Paté, low-grain, complete and balanced wetfood for Puppies and nursing or pregnant mothers

ingredients.ingredients: 69% fresh meat and meat products (min. lamb 12%), 10% fresh salmon, 8,5% rice, plant products, vitamins & minerals.

analysis.analysis: Protein 8%, fat content 6%, crude ash 2%,crude fibre 0.4%, moisture 80%.

feedingRecommendation.feedingRecommendation: Freshwater should always be available. Prior to opening the pack,  it should be stored in dry, cool conditions. After opening, store in an airtight container, keep refrigerated and use it within 72 Hours. The recommended quantities can vary according to breed, seasonal and age factors. Traceability: Best before date/lot no, see can bottom.

nutritionAdditives.nutritionAdditives: Vitamin A 1000IU/kg, Vitamin D3 100IU/kg , Vitamin E 13IU/kg, Zinc (Zinc Sulphate Monohydrate) 5 mg/kg, Manganese (Manganous Sulphate Monohydrate) 2.5 mg/kg, Selenium (Sodium Selenite) 0.03 mg/kg, Iodine (Calcium iodate anhydrous) 0.25 mg/kg, Phosphorus 0.03 mg/kg, Calcium 0.25 mg/kg.

longDescription.longDescription:
Chef’s Choice Lamb and Rice Recipe For Puppies is carefully formulated by chefs and nutritionists to provide the extra energy puppies need in the form of calories, fat and protein to fuel all of their growing, playing and discovering. Our smooth puppy recipe is made with 100% fresh lamb, rice, and natural, wholesome ingredients, while having low-grain, and being free from sugar, salt, artificial colors, aromas or preservatives. This mouth watering recipe is enhanced with vitamins, minerals and other nutrients to make this meal hard to forget. 
You might be cooking your own food but your puppy has a Chef at home.
